## Government Contracting Domain Knowledge

### 18 Entity Types (The Ontology)

| Type | Description | Examples |
|------|-------------|----------|
| `requirement` | Contractual obligations (shall/should/may) | "Contractor shall provide 24/7 support" |
| `clause` | FAR/DFARS regulatory references | "FAR 52.212-4", "DFARS 252.227-7014" |
| `section` | RFP structural elements (A-M, J attachments) | "Section L.3.2", "Attachment J-1" |
| `document` | Referenced documents and standards | "MIL-STD-882E", "PWS Attachment A" |
| `deliverable` | CDRLs and contract deliverables | "Monthly Status Report", "CDRL A001" |
| `evaluation_factor` | Section M scoring criteria | "Technical Approach (40%)" |
| `submission_instruction` | Section L requirements | "Volume I: 50 pages max" |
| `statement_of_work` | SOW/PWS task descriptions | "Task 3.2 Network Operations" |
| `performance_metric` | KPIs and QASP standards | "99.9% uptime SLA" |
| `strategic_theme` | Win themes and hot buttons | "Mission-critical reliability" |
| `organization` | Agencies and contractors | "Naval Air Systems Command" |
| `program` | Government programs | "AFCAP V", "MCPP II" |
| `equipment` | GFE/CFE items | "Government-furnished vehicles" |
| `technology` | Technical systems | "AWS GovCloud" |
| `concept` | Domain terminology | "CONUS operations", "CLIN 0001" |
| `location` | Performance locations | "Joint Base Andrews" |
| `event` | Milestone events | "Contract award: Q2 FY25" |
| `person` | Key personnel | "Contracting Officer" |

### Key Domain Concepts

- **UCF (Uniform Contract Format)**: Sections A-M structure
- **Section L ↔ M Mapping**: Instructions (L) evaluate via factors (M)
- **CDRL**: Contract Data Requirements List (deliverables)
- **FAR/DFARS**: Federal/Defense Acquisition Regulations
- **BOE**: Basis of Estimate (Labor, Materials, ODCs, QA, Logistics, Lifecycle, Compliance)
- **Shipley Methodology**: Capture planning best practices

