## Testing Guidelines

### Quick Validation (Use Before Full Upload)

```powershell
# Event loop fix test (30 seconds)
python test_event_loop.py

# Full Neo4j validation (2-5 minutes)
python test_neo4j_quick.py

# Formal test suite
python -m pytest tests/ -v
```

### Test Naming Convention

```
test_<feature>_<scenario>.py
tests/test_schema_prompts.py
tests/test_workload_enrichment.py
tests/test_deliverable_traceability.py
```

### Baseline Comparison Pattern

```python
# Compare against known-good outputs
BASELINE_ENTITY_COUNT = 339  # From perfect_run_branch_022
assert entity_count >= BASELINE_ENTITY_COUNT * 0.95
assert entity_count <= BASELINE_ENTITY_COUNT * 1.05
```

