## Code Review Checklist

When reviewing or writing code:

- [ ] Type hints on all function parameters and return values
- [ ] Pydantic models for any LLM response parsing
- [ ] Async/await for LLM and Neo4j operations
- [ ] Graceful error handling (log warning, use fallback, don't crash)
- [ ] Logging at appropriate levels (INFO for progress, WARNING for recoverable issues)
- [ ] Entity types from valid 18-type ontology only
- [ ] No hardcoded API keys or credentials
- [ ] Configuration via environment variables (`.env`)

